   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">Cinq titres prÃ©cÃ¨dent le cycle des Rougon-MacquartÂ : <text:span text:style-name="T3">La Confession de Claude</text:span> (1865), <text:span text:style-name="T3">Le VÅu d&apos;une morte</text:span> (1866), <text:span text:style-name="T3">Les MystÃ¨res de Marseille</text:span> (1867), <text:span text:style-name="T3">ThÃ©rÃ¨se Raquin</text:span> (1867) et <text:span text:style-name="T3">Madeleine FÃ©rat</text:span> (1868).</text:p>
